# 🎵 Spotify Web Clone 🎵

Welcome to the *Spotify Web Player Clone, a visually appealing and functional music player UI inspired by Spotify! 🎶 Built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript*, this project aims to replicate the aesthetic and interactive experience of Spotify.

![Spotify Web Clone](pictures/picture.jpg)

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 *Modern UI* - Clean and responsive design.
- 🔍 *Search & Library Section* - Easily explore music and access your library.
- 🎶 *Recently Played & Playlists* - Display curated playlists and top mixes.
- 📊 *Featured Charts* - See what's trending globally.
- 🎛 *Music Player Controls* - Play, pause, skip, and adjust the playback.
- 🌟 *Dark Mode Theme* - Sleek and immersive interface.

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- *HTML5* - Structure of the web page.
- *CSS3* - Styling and responsiveness.
- *JavaScript* - Interactivity and animations.
- *Font Awesome* - Icons for UI enhancement.

